content.text:
import numpy as np
from scipy.io.wavfile import write

# Audio parameters
duration = 10  # seconds
sample_rate = 44100  # Hz
t = np.linspace(0, duration, int(sample_rate * duration), endpoint=False)

# Frequencies to mix
freq1 = 8  # Hz
freq2 = 258  # Hz

# Generate sine waves
wave1 = np.sin(2 * np.pi * freq1 * t)
wave2 = np.sin(2 * np.pi * freq2 * t)

# Mix and normalize
mixed_wave = wave1 + wave2
mixed_wave /= np.max(np.abs(mixed_wave))  # Normalize to -1 to 1
